value.def: A stud is an earring consisting of a small shape attached to a bar which goes through a hole in your ear.
Studs are small round objects attached to the bottom of boots, especially sports boots, so that the person wearing them does not slip.

value.def: Horses or other animals that are kept for stud are kept to be used for breeding.

example.ex: He was voted horse of the year and then was retired to stud.
example.tran: 这匹马被评为年度冠军后就退役成了种马。

value.def: If you refer to a man as a stud, you mean that he is thought to be very active sexually and good at satisfying his partner's sexual desires.
value.tran: 性欲旺盛的男子;风流男子

value.def: A stud is the same as a stud farm .
